基于 JavaScript 所构建的跨平台开发框架.message: Cross-platform development framework built on JavaScript

feature.tsSupport.message: Full support for TypeScript, enhancing development efficiency and safety.
feature.tsSupport.description: 对 TypeScript 的完全支持，提升开发效率与安全性。

feature.frontendEcosystem.message: Can use front-end ecosystems such as React, SCSS, and Tailwind CSS to depict images.
feature.frontendEcosystem.description: 可借助 React、SCSS、Tailwind CSS 等前端生态描绘图片。

feature.developerMode.message: A complete set of standardized robot development modes for quick onboarding.
feature.developerMode.description: 一整套约定的机器人开发模式，快速上手。

feature.startupSpeed.message: Extreme startup speed and execution efficiency, enhancing user experience.
feature.startupSpeed.description: 极致的启动速度和执行效率，提升用户体验。

feature.esBuildRollup.message: Built on esBuild and Rollup for packaging, compression, obfuscation, etc.
feature.esBuildRollup.description: 基于esBuild和Rollup,可打包、压缩、混淆等。

feature.robotDevEcosystem.message: A comprehensive robot development ecosystem and toolchain to assist developers.
feature.robotDevEcosystem.description: 拥有完整的机器人开发生态和工具链，助力开发者。

feature.customIntegration.message: Flexible integration with various platforms, customizable to meet needs.
feature.customIntegration.description: 可扩展、可自定义的对接各类平台，灵活适应需求。

feature.globalControl.message: Control global incoming calls. Adaptable and compatible.
feature.globalControl.description: 控制全局传入调用。可适配可兼容。

feature.debugWithoutLogin.message: Debug and experience the project without logging into any platform.
feature.debugWithoutLogin.description: 不需要登录任何平台即可调试和体验工程。
